description: A solar-powered eating experience unlike any other, SolarCart Cafe is cooking up quality cuisine with a mission to serve environmental responsibility.  Working with local non-profits, their seasonal menu offers a rotating selection of delicious international cuisine, all made with local, organic, and sustainably sourced ingredients. With a percentage of the sales going to their tree planting initiative, you’re sure to love every bite of this food just as much as you’ll love helping to make the world a better place.
name: SolarCart Cafe
